    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for someone looking for a functional, budget-friendly daily driver. While the engine and transmission are in working order and the car is mechanically sound for its age, there is noticeable cosmetic wear both inside and out, including some paint fading and interior scuffs. It has been reliably maintained to ensure it remains roadworthy, though a buyer should expect the typical quirks associated with a used vehicle of this age. This is a solid, no-frills option for dependable transportation.",
