    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to put this beauty up for grabs! Honestly, it is in such stunning, pristine condition that you'd swear it just rolled off the showroom floor. I have babied this car since day one\u2014it's been garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and it drives like an absolute dream. You won't find a single blemish on it! It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it just as much as I have. Trust me, you have to see it in person to believe how perfect it is!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S is a peerless example of the 996.2 generation, featuring the naturally aspirated 3.6L flat-six engine with VarioCam Plus valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise G96 6-speed manual transaxle and an advanced viscous-coupling AWD system. Mechanically flawless, the vehicle has undergone a proactive IMS bearing retrofit and shows zero signs of bore scoring. The chassis remains exceptionally taut, utilizing factory-spec Bilstein dampers and 18-inch Turbo-look II wheels wrapped in N-rated Michelin Pilot Sport rubber. Braking is managed by four-piston monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors, providing immediate, fade-free deceleration. This is a collector-grade specimen with a pristine underbody and factory-tight tolerances throughout.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Clean title. All service records available.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and climate-controlled since new. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with a professional ceramic coating; there are no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin retains its original 'new car' scent, with the premium leather upholstery remaining supple and free of any bolster wear or creasing. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive folder of service records from authorized technicians. The engine bay is detailed and dry, with no signs of aging or fluid seepage. This sale includes all original manuals, two sets of keys, and the window sticker. This is a turn-key collector-grade vehicle for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish complemented by an immaculate, smoke-free interior. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets the most exacting standards of performance and reliability. With a comprehensive service history and negligible signs of use, this offering represents the definitive choice for the discerning buyer seeking a turn-key investment. Experience the pinnacle of pre-owned excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty\u2014it's honestly in showroom condition! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car, so it\u2019s looking and driving just like it did the day it was born. Not a single scratch or smudge to be found, and the interior still has that fresh feel. It\u2019s super clean, incredibly reliable, and ready for a new home. You won\u2019t find another one kept this well, so come grab it before it's gone!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, featuring the legendary 13B-REW rotary powerplant with its complex sequential twin-turbocharger setup functioning flawlessly. This chassis maintains its factory-spec 50:50 weight distribution and remains unmolested, retaining the original Torsen limited-slip differential and aluminum double-wishbone suspension. The apex seals hold excellent compression, and the vacuum routing has been meticulously maintained to ensure linear boost delivery. Zero signs of oxidation on the undercarriage or heat-cycling fatigue in the engine bay. A rare opportunity to acquire a pristine example of 90s JDM engineering with original VIN-matching components.",
